title: Walters Trial Makes up for Lack of Evidence with Drama (Audio)
itunes:title: Walters Trial Makes up for Lack of Evidence with Drama (Audio)
description:
(Bloomberg) -- Peter Henning, a law professor at Wayne State University Law School, discusses the latest updates in the insider trading trial for Las Vegas gambler Billy Walters. He speaks with June Grasso and Greg Stohr on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg Law."

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
